        "context_precision@k": 0.2
      },
      "answer": "TerraVision applies the following post-processing steps to a Gemini-suggested corridor path: \n1. **Path Simplification** to a maximum of 5 waypoints via `simplifyToMaxPoints()`.\n2. **Boundary Clamping** to constrain all coordinates to region bounds via `clampToRegion()`.\n3. **Obstacle Avoidance** to nudge the path around trees and solar features.\n4. **Deduplication** to remove points closer than 0.00008 decimal degrees (~9m) via `deduplicatePoints()`.\n\n[terra_vision.md #2]\n[terra_vision.md #2]\n[terra_vision.md #2]\n[terra_vision.md #2]",
